Name: Death Cube
About the game: 'Death Cube' is a 2D platformer where you need to cross a room full of obstacles to get to the exit. Spikes, saws, projectiles and lasers, survive through these obstacles and reach at the end of the level. And Remember... DO NOT KILL THE CUBE
